00:03:08.470 --> 00:03:18.691
Sister Lynn—I would encourage every one of you to go and watch Sister Lynn Hammond's message today, this morning at 10 o'clock at the prayer conference here at Branson.

00:03:32.280 --> 00:03:34.240
