00:05:29.943 --> 00:05:36.731
He's coming as we see the signs of the times, watching all around us right now as we speak.

00:05:36.731 --> 00:05:40.480
Jesus Christ is getting ready to come back.

00:05:41.080 --> 00:05:45.760
And I can feel—I have such an anticipation.

00:05:45.760 --> 00:05:50.994
Sister Lynn was talking about how we're going to pray into that.

00:05:50.994 --> 00:06:07.670
And it was cool because when you hear a general like that talking about the prayer things that we're doing, that I've learned by myself and she's probably learned by herself over the years, but I have nobody teaching me.

00:06:13.333 --> 00:06:13.647
We just go down the road, me, Diana and I.

00:06:16.753 --> 00:06:17.220
And I told you that there are rooms.

00:06:17.220 --> 00:06:23.893
When you're praying in the spirit, there are actual rooms that you go into and you unlock when you're praying.

00:06:27.086 --> 00:06:29.856
And it was amazing because she started teaching that today.

00:06:29.856 --> 00:06:36.710
And I said, 'I've never heard anybody teach this before,' because I've only gotten this by—I know when certain people are there.

00:06:36.710 --> 00:06:49.848
And I told you, if you go back and watch my last videos, it's like you know who's praying with you, and you become familiar with that person in the spirit realm.

00:06:49.848 --> 00:06:55.680
My mouth's getting dry, but you get familiar with that person.

00:06:55.680 --> 00:07:20.053
So when you start praying, you know that there's somebody—for instance, she prays for North Korea a lot, and the concentration camps with the Christians that are put in these work concentration camps, and she'll pray and she'll intercede for these people of North Korea, these Asian people that are being treated so terribly.

00:07:24.225 --> 00:07:44.260
And so I thought it was really cool because, you know, when we go in the spirit, we start praying for the people in Nigeria whenever the Lord was showing us the—thank you, hun, well, you don't have a green screen so you can see this is probably my water—the persecution that's coming over the Nigerian people.

00:07:44.260 --> 00:07:49.263
And when we were interceding for them, I saw the mothers and the children and the fathers.

00:07:49.263 --> 00:07:57.863
Remember, if you go back in that video, we went into heavy travail, praying for the protection of the Nigerian people.

00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:05.080
And so, oh, and then I got this—I don't know this lady's name.

