00:08:12.356 --> 00:08:15.093
She could only do this by the Spirit of God.

00:08:19.695 --> 00:08:19.940
I think her name was Jennifer.

00:08:19.940 --> 00:08:20.920
Jennifer, thanks, love.

00:08:22.120 --> 00:08:22.780
I know her name was Jennifer.

00:08:22.780 --> 00:08:26.280
Diana told me—I did not know—but I'm saying she made this quilt.

00:08:30.790 --> 00:08:31.260
Do you remember, Lucy, when I told you she was sitting on a quilt?

00:08:33.220 --> 00:08:41.580
