00:09:41.900 --> 00:09:44.216
Yeah, don't say the last name.

00:09:44.216 --> 00:09:46.000
Special, handmade by Jennifer.

00:09:46.840 --> 00:09:48.728
That was so nice of her.

00:09:48.728 --> 00:09:50.400
She didn't put her last name.

00:09:50.400 --> 00:09:53.800
So, super, super, super sweet people.

00:09:57.760 --> 00:10:00.267
I just thought, I'll cherish this for the rest of my life.

00:10:00.267 --> 00:10:07.725
This is something that, because of something I saw in heaven, I had something tangible to touch.

00:10:07.725 --> 00:10:19.571
I carried it with me to the altar today when I was praying for the people because I thought, I want to get the anointing all over this.

00:10:25.155 --> 00:10:34.090
And I thought, you know, if I can, when the anointing comes on me, I want to put my hands on it and lay hands on this and let that anointing transfer because it goes into cloth.

00:10:36.970 --> 00:10:41.129
And I told D, I said, 'I want to saturate this thing,' because I use it with my prayer shawl a lot.

00:10:41.129 --> 00:10:47.566
But I thought, this is something so special to me now.

00:10:47.566 --> 00:10:53.173
I'm going to carry it with me everywhere because I just love it.

00:10:53.173 --> 00:11:01.360
I really, truly do, and I'll let Megan hold it.

00:11:01.360 --> 00:11:17.055
But I just thought, what somebody took so much time to stitch this for me, and it really meant a lot because she got something out of the spirit, and she got it to a T.

00:11:19.531 --> 00:11:19.914
And that's why I thought, look at that.

00:11:19.914 --> 00:11:27.150
Only by the Spirit of God could somebody do that and do the colors and all the beautifulness of it.

00:11:29.060 --> 00:11:29.347
And I thought, isn't that wonderful?

00:11:29.347 --> 00:11:31.520
I don't know.

00:11:31.520 --> 00:11:37.531
I just love it when people do stuff like that.

00:11:37.531 --> 00:11:41.090
I just thought, look at that.

00:11:41.090 --> 00:11:42.289
Isn't that wonderful?

00:11:53.600 --> 00:11:53.920
So, I'll let you see my little treasure I got today.

00:11:53.920 --> 00:11:59.900
But there's a lot going on, and I know I say that a lot.

00:11:59.900 --> 00:12:07.131
That's where we are right now in the signs of the times.

00:12:07.726 --> 00:12:11.150
I told Diana, I said, 'Look at what happened today.

00:12:11.150 --> 00:12:13.773
' Look at what happened yesterday.

00:12:21.189 --> 00:12:21.674
We have such an acceleration of things like we've never seen before.

00:12:21.674 --> 00:12:27.880
Watching the fig tree, calling for peace with the Abrahamic Accords and acceleration of war.

00:12:27.880 --> 00:12:32.020
You know, Putin has called for a meeting with President Trump in Hungary.

00:12:32.020 --> 00:12:32.640
Hungary.

00:12:32.640 --> 00:12:33.280
Did I say that right?

00:12:33.280 --> 00:12:33.920
Hungary.

00:12:33.920 --> 00:12:34.560
Hungary.

00:12:50.160 --> 00:12:50.360
I don't know, I probably butchered the name.

00:12:50.360 --> 00:12:55.120
But he's called for a meeting.

00:12:55.120 --> 00:12:59.832
So, what is that meeting going to entail?

00:12:59.832 --> 00:13:05.480
He's saying he's going to put pressure on them to cause peace in Ukraine.

00:13:05.480 --> 00:13:07.400
But will this poke the bear?

00:13:07.400 --> 00:13:12.867
You know, I saw the Tomahawk missiles flying into Moscow and a great escalation of war.

00:13:12.867 --> 00:13:22.697
Now, I see in part here and in part there, and not everything, when I'm praying in the spirit and the Lord is showing us and revealing to us what we're praying about.

00:13:22.697 --> 00:13:28.585
Some of it is to stop, to lessen, or some of it can't be.

00:13:33.049 --> 00:13:34.320
And we're praying for the protection of the innocent, for lives not to be lost.

00:13:44.137 --> 00:13:54.337
And so, you know, I still feel in my heart that this thing is really going to kick off to another level as I've been praying into it.

00:13:54.337 --> 00:14:18.760
But what we have been really focusing on, even now, Diana and I and Braden, when we're praying, even when we came over here because we had all that time in the car, I went into deep intercession, into travail, praying over—how, Lord, help me, I want to get the right words—bringing in the closers.

00:14:18.760 --> 00:14:27.360
And the Lord said to me, he said, "Brandon, you are about to see a phase of the elders again.

00:14:38.600 --> 00:14:38.840
We're getting to that point where you'll see the elders start to go home.

00:14:41.440 --> 00:14:42.669
" And he said, "I'm bringing in my closers.

00:14:42.669 --> 00:14:45.754
I'm bringing in my closers.

00:14:46.200 --> 00:14:51.629
" And I said, "Well, Lord, what is it about the closers?

00:14:51.629 --> 00:14:51.971
What is this?

00:15:04.086 --> 00:15:04.480
" And he says, "Study about it.

00:15:04.480 --> 00:15:06.665
" So Diana starts doing her research.

00:15:07.820 --> 00:15:11.040
The closers are the ones that handle all the pressure.

00:15:11.040 --> 00:15:18.551
Whenever they get put on the mound to throw the baseball and they're getting ready to close the baseball game, they don't want to lose their lead.

00:15:27.274 --> 00:15:27.600
They don't want to lose their momentum in the game.

00:15:27.600 --> 00:15:32.606
So, they put somebody in that is like a warrior, somebody who is broken.

00:15:32.606 --> 00:15:39.453
They put the warhorse in that is not going to be moved by all the bombs going off and all the craziness, right?

00:15:41.240 --> 00:15:44.870
So, you put somebody in that has nerves of steel.

00:15:44.870 --> 00:15:48.120
You put somebody in that is born for pressure.

00:15:48.120 --> 00:15:52.943
And the Lord said to me, "Brandon, I'm putting in the closers.

00:16:08.610 --> 00:16:08.900
" And I told Diana, I said, "So, when he's talking about us, ladies and gentlemen, he means that we are made for this time.

00:16:08.900 --> 00:16:17.466
None of this is going to shake us or get us off our game because we're the closers.

00:16:17.466 --> 00:16:19.636
We have been designed.

00:16:19.636 --> 00:16:32.550
We have been foreordained—you know, when I told everybody that we're on that olive press and that we're the olives, and the olives are being pressed and pressed and pressed right now.

00:16:37.491 --> 00:16:38.589
And he said, 'Brandon, that oil is going to start to flow from that olive press.

00:16:38.589 --> 00:16:41.150
With persecution comes great olive oil with the press.

00:16:41.150 --> 00:16:44.253
' And the Lord warned us about all that.

00:16:44.253 --> 00:16:47.490
And so, that's what I have been praying into.

00:16:51.796 --> 00:16:52.007
All hands on deck, getting people ready for what's about to happen.

00:16:52.007 --> 00:17:06.565
When I went to the church and I wore the pink shorts and I prayed more into that, the Lord said, 'See, what I'm trying to tell you is you need to have less fear of man and more fear of me regardless of what I tell you to do.

00:17:06.565 --> 00:17:10.960
Even if it sounds crazy to you, obey me at all costs.

00:17:10.960 --> 00:17:17.240
Even if I tell you to wear a green shirt with polka dots, do you understand?

00:17:17.240 --> 00:17:18.920
It's not about the clothes.

00:17:18.920 --> 00:17:24.385
It's about humility and doing what he told you to do.

00:17:24.385 --> 00:17:28.430
' Like Mary said, whatever he tells you to do, do it.

00:17:28.430 --> 00:17:31.789
Whatever he tells you to do, do it.

00:17:35.440 --> 00:17:36.720
And that's what the Lord was showing me with the pink shorts.

00:17:36.720 --> 00:17:39.074
It wasn't about the pink shorts.

00:17:39.074 --> 00:17:45.026
It was about obedience, even when you worry about what everybody else thinks around you.

00:17:47.152 --> 00:17:55.347
And that's me dying to that—worried about comment sections, worried about emails, worried about just any knucklehead that comes on there telling you what they think and how they think you should do it better or whatever.

00:17:55.347 --> 00:17:57.754
Following the voice of God at all costs.

00:17:57.754 --> 00:18:05.160
No matter what you feel, no matter what you see or what you think, listen to him and listen again.

00:18:05.160 --> 00:18:09.389
Follow the voice of God.

00:18:14.310 --> 00:18:14.565
And that's what I'm trying to tell you all where we are right now.

00:18:15.840 --> 00:18:25.320
The warhorses have those blinders on their eyes and they're not looking at what's going on with the missile going over here or somebody falling over there.

00:18:25.320 --> 00:18:32.759
They're just focused on the task at hand, following the voice of their instructor.

00:18:32.759 --> 00:18:37.540
Turn, go this way, go high, faster, faster, whatever.

00:18:37.540 --> 00:18:42.209
They're listening to the man on the horse, to their rider.

00:18:42.209 --> 00:18:52.860
So, what we're doing right now is listening to our Father, and we are that horse that is broken before the Lord.

00:18:59.710 --> 00:18:59.945
And the Lord told me, he said, 'Brandon, you're a closer.

00:18:59.945 --> 00:19:09.760
These people on this YouTube channel, I have called them to the kingdom for such a time as this, to bring the lost in, to bring in the unsaved.

00:19:09.760 --> 00:19:19.298
You're running out of time and you're going to see an escalation of things as we see the days approach and they're evil.

00:19:25.171 --> 00:19:27.240
The darkness is going to get darker, but the light is going to get lighter in the church.

00:19:27.240 --> 00:19:42.909
' And that's what he was trying to show me—no matter what you step into, like I was at a really amazing church, but he said, 'Go in there with pink shorts on.

00:19:42.909 --> 00:19:49.110
' And I'm going back to that because it's not about what they say.

00:19:50.996 --> 00:19:51.307
It's about what I say.

00:19:51.307 --> 00:19:52.960
Do what I tell you to do.

00:19:52.960 --> 00:19:58.686
Do what I tell you to do and do it with all your heart.

00:19:58.686 --> 00:20:16.590
Whatever you do in word and deed, do all to the glory of God, even if you think it makes you look foolish.

00:20:16.590 --> 00:20:20.920
So, that's what a warhorse would do, and that's what a closer would do.

00:20:20.920 --> 00:20:25.412
It's not about the pressure.

00:20:25.412 --> 00:20:28.060
So, that's what I've been praying into.

00:20:28.060 --> 00:20:43.180
That's been my assignment over the last week, praying for the people that have a backbone like a crowbar, that will not sway when the opinions of man come, because I'm telling you, great persecution is coming.

00:20:43.180 --> 00:20:46.223
Great persecution is coming to the church.

00:20:49.945 --> 00:20:50.270
And the Lord said, 'A shaking to awaken is coming.

00:20:50.270 --> 00:20:54.030
' And so, I talked to Pastor Paul Begley.

00:20:54.500 --> 00:21:02.305
He had me on his YouTube broadcast, and he recorded me, and he wanted me to be for some seminar that he's doing.

00:21:02.305 --> 00:21:12.893
And so, I talked for over an hour, and I gave him 20 prophetic words that have been stirring in my spirit for the last year and what I believe is coming.

00:21:12.893 --> 00:21:24.160
Some of it, like I said, you know, he called me a prophet and everything and said about Kim Clement and all that, and that's a great honor, but I truly do not see myself as a prophet.

00:21:29.735 --> 00:21:34.312
I see myself as a watchman, but I don't ever correct people, I just keep going.

00:21:34.312 --> 00:21:44.720
But you know me, y'all, I really truly believe that God has called me to be a prayer warrior.

00:21:44.720 --> 00:21:58.271
He even said—because my main thing, I was so excited because I love to go around these healing ministries, go around with Billy Burke and see healing and do things.

00:22:13.884 --> 00:22:22.800
And the Lord said to me, 'I know you really enjoy this, I know you do'—because I'm like, 'I want to go again because I love to see people get blessed like that'—but he said, 'That's not your main vein.

00:22:23.920 --> 00:22:28.000
Your main vein is intercessory prayer, and that's what I've called you to.

00:22:32.377 --> 00:22:32.663
So, you've got to go around the prayer people now.

00:22:32.663 --> 00:22:37.600
Go over here and get around your brothers and your sisters that know how to intercede.

00:22:37.600 --> 00:22:42.200
' So, that's what we're here in Branson doing now.

00:22:48.115 --> 00:22:48.360
And all glory to God.

00:22:48.360 --> 00:22:55.679
And thank you all for always supporting us and being so kind to my family with these super thanks.

00:23:00.278 --> 00:23:03.270
I see them going up.

00:23:03.280 --> 00:23:05.360
And you all are just so kind.

00:23:05.360 --> 00:23:07.360
You're so kind to Diana and me.

00:23:07.360 --> 00:23:12.165
And we want to say thank you from the bottom of our hearts.

00:23:17.613 --> 00:23:19.400
You don't realize how much you've changed our life by freeing us up.

00:23:30.560 --> 00:23:30.880
We don't have to worry about eBay and be able to say, "Hey, listen.

00:23:30.880 --> 00:23:35.947
We can go to this conference and stay a couple of days.

00:23:37.411 --> 00:23:46.231
" And whenever I was going through all the spiritual warfare that I went through for the last couple of weeks, it has been incredible.

00:23:58.406 --> 00:24:00.048
But the Lord, I'm telling you, remember I told you the last time, I said when you get underneath that anointing and that wave of the glory keeps washing you, it keeps knocking you.

00:24:21.659 --> 00:24:22.640
And I'm telling you, that thing that's in your life has an expiration date.

00:24:22.640 --> 00:24:34.791
No matter how dark you think your circumstances are, or even like whenever you have weeks like we had, there's an expiration date to your problems.

00:24:34.791 --> 00:24:38.084
When you're walking through the valley, you don't camp there.

00:24:38.084 --> 00:24:43.406
When you're walking through the valley of the shadow of death, you don't camp there.

00:24:45.034 --> 00:24:49.493
You get a recreational vehicle, you put it in four-wheel drive, and you keep going.

00:24:49.756 --> 00:24:51.020
